<p>On the same occasion, Enrico Aditjondro, Associate Director for Advocacy, Policy, and Communication for Vital Strategies revealed the collaboration between his organization and Muhammadiyah, especially UMY and UMM, began in 2016 at Code River. &#8220;There are so many potentials that we can explore from this collaboration. We are honored to be able to cooperate with UMY and UMM, and hopefully we can continue to work together,&#8221; he added. (ays)</p>
